text.section:
The Fund shall consist of:
premiums for coverage that the Plan issues;
money collected in accordance with § 19-219 of the Health - General Article;
money deposited by a nonprofit health service plan in accordance with § 14-513 of this subtitle;
income from investments that the Board makes or authorizes on behalf of the Fund;
interest on deposits or investments of money from the Fund;
premium tax revenue collected under § 14-107 of this title;
money collected by the Board as a result of legal or other actions taken by the Board on behalf of the Fund;
money donated to the Fund; and
money awarded to the Fund through grants.
